'''2014年格羅茲尼爆炸事件'''（'''2014 Grozny bombing'''）是一起發生在[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]][[車臣共和國|車臣共和國]]首府[[格羅茲尼|格羅茲尼]]的[[恐怖攻擊|恐怖攻擊]]事件。2014年10月5日，19歲的男子奧普提·穆達羅夫（Opti Mudarov）前往市政廳參加一場慶祝格羅茲尼之日與車臣共和國總統[[拉姆贊·卡德羅夫|拉姆贊·卡德羅夫]]生日的集會，當安檢警方發現他舉止不尋常而將他攔下搜身時，男子引爆身上的炸彈，造成自身及五名警察喪生，並有12人遭到波及而受傷<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-29498909|title=Five killed in suicide bombing in Chechen capital|work=BBC News|accessdate=2014-11-07|archive-date=2014-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110210819/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-29498909|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.euronews.com/2014/10/05/police-officers-killed-in-suicide-bomb-attack-in-chechnya/ |title=Police officers killed in suicide bomb attack in Chechnya |accessdate=2014-12-04 |archive-date=2014-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141213013102/http://www.euronews.com/2014/10/05/police-officers-killed-in-suicide-bomb-attack-in-chechnya/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sbs.com.au/news/article/2014/10/06/suicide-bomb-kills-five-police-chechnya|title=Suicide bomb kills five police in Chechnya|work=News|accessdate=2014-11-07|archive-date=2014-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141203202520/http://www.sbs.com.au/news/article/2014/10/06/suicide-bomb-kills-five-police-chechnya|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

